'''Lee Gi-hyuk''' ({{Korean|이기혁}}; born 7 July 2000) is a South Korean professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Centre-back|centre-back]] or a [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|left-back]] for [[Gangwon FC]] and the [[South Korea national football team|South Korea national team]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://kleague.com/record/playerDetail.do?playerId=20210104 |title=Profile |accessdate=2 October 2022 |publisher=kleague.com |language=Korean}}</ref>

